            </p>
            <p>
                For assistance with Webtrieve or more information, please contact your ALS Tribology office.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr />
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="carousel-container span6">
            <div id="home-carousel" class="carousel slide">
                <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                    <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
